{"tid":199076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"配合聯國制裁 台灣已禁北韓煤礦進口","createTime":"2017-04-13T02:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T15:08:51.000Z","uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3020878c9004cac2661e1cf7f1b837ede62249c7","tid":199076,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"〔記者呂伊萱、黃佩君／台北報導〕北韓頻頻試射飛彈，東北亞情勢升溫，我國外交部次長李澄然昨在立法院受訪時表示，台灣作為國際社會負責任成員，希望區域維持穩定，也配合聯合國安理會決議，實施對北韓的制裁措施，例如不從北韓進口煤礦等。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/apr/13/images/bigPic/400_400/314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fapr%2F13%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F314.jpg&h=6b21d518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經濟部貿易局表示，台灣自二○○六年起就配合安理會決議，暫停自北韓輸出入產品措施，本次則是配合安理會去年十一月決議，於三月九日預告包含煤礦、鐵礦石、黃金、稀土礦等卅五項產品暫停自北韓進口。其實，北韓煤礦自去年三月起就未再進口。<br />\n除配合安理會決議外，我國貿易法也規定有戰略性高科技貨品輸出管制清單，納入國際性反精密武器擴散至特定國家的「瓦聖那協議清單」及「防止擴散清單」內之輸出貨品，管制對北韓及伊朗兩國出口貨品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1093760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1093760&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4FKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=a9174c04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1093760&h=5f5791e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1093760</a>"},{"pid":"d5352e03354c9bcfc654929afb1ab5b63d28777a","tid":199076,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"似真黎料"},{"pid":"63929c36516a101357bcce1490076179aaf20e35","tid":199076,"uid":9958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"都唔受你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bcc7c1f9ed84154192950a1a962c98c98ccaab","tid":199076,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" clas